data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. This exquisite golf and waterfront Eagle Creek Golf clubhouse offers luxurious finishes and living space. This spacious four-bedroom, four full-bath home has a soaring 10-foot ceiling as you enter and welcomes you with a beautiful water and golf view located at the 15th hole. The living room leads you to a large lanai, overlooking a tranquil backyard with a spectacular resort-like heated salt pool offering plenty of privacy and peace to enjoy entertaining in all types of Florida weather! The open floor plan allows for a large and breathtaking gourmet kitchen with upgraded cabinets, and appliances and a large island perfect for family gatherings. This home features a large primary bedroom with a spectacular view, tray ceilings, a large custom walk-in closet and a large primary bath. The second floor has two additional bedrooms and a den with upgraded flooring, and balcony deck. Relax on your balcony and enjoy your gorgeous pool surrounded by a green and blooming garden and incredible sunrise! This luxury property resides in Eagle Creek, home to a top-of-its-class golf course with amenities such as community pools, playgrounds, dog parks, tennis courts, basketball courts, a fitness center, clubhouse with amazing food and more! Just minutes from Lake Nona Medical City, the VA hospital, Nemours Children's Hospital, Lake Nona Town Center, Boxi Park Lake Nona, USTA national campus, KPMG and Orlando International  Airport.  <iframe width='853' height='480' src='https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=u7uV52PLe88' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen allow='xr-spatial-tracking'></iframe>
